{"tid":991844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工返到個人好頹，唉！","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T16:54:02.000Z","uid":98868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d67aadbe342b716adcfcba1c39eba91aede62db3","tid":991844,"uid":98868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"小弟畢業左5年<br />\n第一份工就做左3年半<br />\n但最近呢一年半 無份做得長<br />\n前前後後換左3份<br />\n開始有d唔知自己想點<br />\n<br />\n本身第一工屬於半公務員 <br />\n但調左去一個唔太適合ge department <br />\n拎完酬金就走左<br />\n<br />\n又做下私人大半年 <br />\n然後而家返緊part time <br />\n開頭係好爽 鐘意返就報更 <br />\n唔鐘意就係屋企煲劇食炒面王<br />\n可以兩三日都唔落街<br />\n兩老都有返工 唔太需要家用<br />\n<br />\n但開始覺得個人好頹<br />\n唔知自己想點<br />\n有無巴打屌醒下我 or 有無頹巴一齊圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a538a45acceb1863399bf835c83d9c764ebcb5ce","tid":991844,"uid":98868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"今晚返通宵 收8點 仲有成7個鐘先收工<br />\n唉 漫漫長夜。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556b45f977a377ff7080765429871426e4bba332","tid":991844,"uid":141285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"返咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b709c1ffe81d2156fdbf53693024e9ce1bc2a82","tid":991844,"uid":98868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556b45f977a377ff7080765429871426e4bba332","tid":991844,"uid":141285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"返咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"齋坐 玩電話 等收工<br />\n同保安無乜分別 係人工高少少<br />\n你當高級保安啦"},{"pid":